The &quot;leak&quot; is probably just a side effect of the exception, because the code as written is not exception-safe. Use try-with-resources to manage the ArrowRecordBatch instead of manually calling `close()`:

```java
try (ArrowRecordBatch batch = unloader.getRecordBatch()) {
    loader.load(batch);
}
```

(though, depending on what `load` does, this may not be enough).

